{"tid":2131890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（已經唔存在？）亞投行年會 習近平未提大撒幣及「一帶一路」","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T07:24:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9ee98cebef525da904fdeec6d2caec7bae0714","tid":2131890,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:31:44.000Z","msg":"由中國國家主席習近平一手成立的「亞洲基礎設施投資銀行（亞投行）」，本月28日舉行第5屆年會，受到疫情影響，採取視訊會議方式進行，習近平在開幕式中發表講話，但是，外界觀察到，習近平在講話中，隻字未提「一帶一路」，也未提任何的大撒幣援助計劃，反而提「多邊主義」、合作等，被認為是習近平的擴張政策受到嚴重挫敗，且曝露出中國經濟已面臨到「自身難保」的窘境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3243994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3243994&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=9bb0828c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3243994&h=8089fe6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3243994</a>"},{"pid":"ea2781ed33f7b079e889934a10504525f33446e1","tid":2131890,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"係囉，第一個反應點解唔講一帶一路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ce86fc94f21369515adcc967508558e87769a3","tid":2131890,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea2781ed33f7b079e889934a10504525f33446e1","tid":2131890,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"係囉，第一個反應點解唔講一帶一路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"入咗《一帶一路》嘅國家都開始違約同無錢還，仲有傻仔落搭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dcf219eb8da1f435e174387e857e066ecb8afa","tid":2131890,"uid":39200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy